transcript:
Hello?
Executive: Bolo madam.
Customer: Ji sir, main Nancy baat kar rahi thi aapke account manager. Sir, wo products vagera sare addition ho gaye the kal hi aur aapka jo naam tha na company name aur aapka naam likh ke aa raha tha wo bhi ho gaya.
Executive: Haan haan.
Customer: Theek hai? Dekhta ek 10 minute mein aur ring karta hu.
Executive: Theek hai sir, kariye fir main close kar deti hu yahan se.
Customer: Theek hai.
Executive: Contact close.
